dct_title_s: A topographical map of the counties of Bergen, Hudson and Essex with parts of Passaic and Union ; from original surveys and levelings, supplemented by various local surveys, based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Atlas sheet No. 7 (Northeastern Red Sandstone)." Originally issued folded in covers 24 x 17 cm.
